 transitions could permit measurement of the dark matter's quantum\nnumbers; for wino-like dark matter, such photons are rare, but might be\nobservable by a future ground-based gamma-ray telescope combining large\neffective area and a low energy threshold.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Oct 2016 20:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2017 17:17:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2022 16:02:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-20"}
