y that is consistent with the values\nrecovered by the observational analysis algorithms. Both the synthetic\nobservations and the product datacubes are public and can be found in the\ncollaboration website http://astro.ft.uam.es/selgifs/data_challenge/.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Oct 2016 20:00:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Jun 2018 20:21:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 8 Jun 2018 17:21:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-04"}
