 value of 42.8=/-2.1 ms acquired with the previous\nbright blood technique. Conclusion: This study validated the application of a\nsingle breathhold black blood single shot fast spin echo acquisition based for\nhuman liver T1rho imaging. The lower liver parenchyma T1rho value and higher\nscan rescan reproducibility may improve of the sensitivity of this technique.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2016 07:46:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-26"}
