erical\ndata confirm the validity of the proposed rescaling with the effective\nCapillary number.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2016 09:32:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 27 Jan 2018 06:43:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-30"}
