a prototype for future experiments requiring a high-intensity\nmuon beam, such as a muon collider or neutrino factory, or the search for rare\nmuon decays which would be a signature for phenomena beyond the Standard Model\nof particle physics. Such a muon beam can also be used in other branches of\nphysics, nuclear and condensed matter, as well as other areas of scientific\nresearch.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2016 12:41:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-05"}
